# 🚨 Theft Detector Android App (Arduino + IR Sensor)

## 📌 Overview

This project is a real-time **Theft Detection System** using **Arduino Uno + IR Sensor + Android App**.
It detects motion and instantly alerts the user via a mobile application.

---

## ⚙️ Hardware Used

* Arduino Uno
* IR Sensor (Motion Detection)
* Buzzer
* USB Cable / OTG

---

## 📱 Features

* Real-time motion detection
* Instant alert on Android app
* Buzzer alarm system
* Simple and clean UI
* USB Serial communication

---

## 🔌 Working

1. IR Sensor detects motion
2. Arduino sends `"ALERT"` via Serial
3. Android app reads data
4. App displays:

   * 🚨 INTRUSION DETECTED
   * ✅ SAFE

---

## 🧠 Tech Stack

* Arduino (C++)
* Android (Java)
* USB Serial Communication

---

## 📸 Output

* When motion detected → 🚨 Alert shown
* When no motion → ✅ Safe

---

## 🚀 Future Improvements

* Bluetooth connectivity (no OTG needed)
* Push notifications
* Firebase logging
* Camera integration

